description: The Consumer Staples Select Sector SPDR Fund seeks to provide investment results that, before expenses, correspond generally to the price and yield performance of the Consumer Staples Select Sector Index (the “Index”)The Index seeks to provide an effective representation of the consumer staples sector of the S&P 500 IndexSeeks to provide precise exposure to companies from consumer staples distribution & retail; household products; food products; beverages; tobacco; and personal care products industries in the U.S.Allows investors to take strategic or tactical positions at a more targeted level than traditional style based investing
name: The Consumer Staples Select Sector SPDR Fund
